                                        <p class="draft-line line-2">
                                            Would love to sync on the roadmap.
                                            <span class="highlight-text">I'm free Thursday 2-4pm or Friday morning</span>
                                            â€” either works great for me.
                                        </p>
                                        <p class="draft-line line-3">
                                            Let me know what suits you best and I'll send over an invite.
                                        </p>
                                        <p class="draft-line line-4 draft-signature">Cheers!</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Action buttons -->
                                <div class="compose-actions">
                                    <button class="btn-send">
                                        <svg
                                            width="16"
                                            height="16"
                                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                            fill="currentColor"
